</div>
<div id=3D"expander-content-1641779954" class=3D"expand-content">
<h1 id=3D"Application-Fixloginatthemiddleofcloudinit"><strong>Fix login at =
the middle of cloud init</strong></h1>
<h2 id=3D"Application-Modificationstouserdata.yml"><strong>Modifications to=
 </strong><code>userdata.yml</code></h2>
<h3 id=3D"Application-1.LateCommands(ExecutedAfterInstallationCompletes)"><=
strong>1. Late Commands (Executed After Installation Completes)</strong></h=
3>
<p>Modify <code>appliance/image/ubuntu/build/userdata.yml</code> under <cod=
e>late-commands</code> to ensure the <code>getty@tty1.service</code> is dis=
abled during post-installation:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">late-co=
mmands:
  - curtin in-target --target=3D/target -- systemctl disable getty@tty1.ser=
vice
  - curtin in-target --target=3D/target -- systemctl daemon-reload</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"Application-2.UserData(Post-InstallationCommands)"><strong>2. Use=
r Data (Post-Installation Commands)</strong></h3>
<p>Modify <code>appliance/image/ubuntu/build/userdata.yml</code> under <cod=
e>user-data/runcmd</code> to re-enable <code>getty@tty1.service</code> afte=
r installation and reboot the system:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">user-da=
ta:
  runcmd:
    - systemctl enable getty@tty1.service
    - reboot</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"Application-BuildingtheISOUsingappliance_ubuntu_branchPipeline"><=
strong>Building the ISO Using </strong><code>appliance_ubuntu_branch</code>=
<strong> Pipeline</strong></h2>
<h3 id=3D"Application-StepstoTriggertheBuild:"><strong>Steps to Trigger the=
 Build:</strong></h3>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p><strong>Ensure Correct Branch Selection:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><code>appliance_branch</code>: As specified in the JIRA.</p></li>
<li>
<p><code>sky_job</code>: Use the current master branch.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Mark </strong><code>upgrade_packages</code><strong> as enabled</=
strong>, as there is a known bug.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Start the Build Pipeline.</strong></p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Wait for the Build to Complete.</strong></p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Download the Generated </strong><code>.iso</code><strong> File</=
strong> from the archived artifacts of the job.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"Application-DeployingtheISOonESXi"><strong>Deploying the ISO on E=
SXi</strong></h2>
<h3 id=3D"Application-1.LogintoESXi:"><strong>1. Log in to ESXi:</strong></=
h3>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Use the following credentials:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Username:</strong> <code>tomer</code></p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Password:</strong> (local password)</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"Application-2.ConfiguretheVirtualMachine:"><strong>2. Configure t=
he Virtual Machine:</strong></h3>
<h4 id=3D"Application-a)ForceBIOSSetup"><strong>a) Force BIOS Setup</strong=
></h4>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Navigate to the VM.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Click <strong>Edit =E2=86=92 VM Options =E2=86=92 Boot Options</strong>.=
</p></li>
<li>
<p>Enable <strong>Force BIOS Setup on Boot</strong>.</p></li>
</ol>
<h4 id=3D"Application-b)UploadtheISOFile"><strong>b) Upload the ISO File</s=
trong></h4>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Navigate to <strong>Edit =E2=86=92 Virtual Hardware</strong>.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Upload the <code>.iso</code> file to the correct directory.</p></li>
<li>
<p><strong>Unmark the "Connect" checkbox</strong> to prevent immediate boot=
.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Restart the VM and enter the BIOS.</p></li>
</ol>
<h4 id=3D"Application-c)StartInstallation"><strong>c) Start Installation</s=
trong></h4>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Select the uploaded ISO.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Choose <strong>"Server Installation"</strong> when prompted.</p></li>
</ol>
<h2 id=3D"Application-Troubleshooting"><strong>Troubleshooting</strong></h2=
>
<h3 id=3D"Application-1.NetworkIssues(ConnectingtotheInternet)"><strong>1. =
Network Issues (Connecting to the Internet)</strong></h3>
<p>If the VM does not connect to the internet, modify the Netplan configura=
tion:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Open the network configuration file:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo na=
no /etc/netplan/50-cloud-init.yaml</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li>
<p>Ensure the following configuration is present:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">network=
:
  ethernets:
    ens160:
      dhcp4: true
      dhcp-identifier: mac
      dhcp6: false</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li>
<p>Apply the changes:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">sudo ne=
tplan apply</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li>
<p>Verify the new IP address:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">ifconfi=
g</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ol>
<h3 id=3D"Application-2.CheckingInstallationLogs"><strong>2. Checking Insta=
llation Logs</strong></h3>
<p>To review the terminal output of the installation process:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">cat /ro=
ot/appliance_installation.log</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p>This structured guide ensures clarity and smooth execution of the entire=
 process.</p>
<p></p>
</div>
</div>
